result.content: Hello everybody! I am a beginner competitive programmer and I just finished the semester, so I have about 4 months to improve my skills. I found the following plan https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_dc3Ifg7Gg1LxhiqMMmE9UbTsXpdRiYh4pKILYG2eA4/edit. Is it a good plan to follow in order to improve significantly? Do you have any other suggestions? Thanks!
